OL,5, A Sheffield Wednesday supporter who    
OL,6, taunted rival fans by mocking the death
OL,7, of Bradley Lowery has been given a     
OL,8, 12-week suspended prison sentence.     
OL,10,FDale Houghton, 32, from Rotherham, was 
OL,11,Fseen laughing as he held up an image of
OL,12,Fthe six-year-old at a match against    
OL,13,FSunderland - the team Bradley supported
OL,14,Fbefore he died of cancer in 2017.      
OL,16,FHoughton, who admitted a public order  
OL,17,Foffence, was also banned from attending
OL,18,Fany football match for five years.     
OL,20,FHis actions were branded "disgraceful".
